# Integration Test Environment Variables (Local Override)
#
# Copy this file to .env.integration.local and fill in your actual CloudPayments test credentials.
# The .env.integration.local file is gitignored and will NOT be committed.
#
# These values override the defaults in api.env for local development with real CloudPayments webhooks.

# ===================================================================
# CLOUDPAYMENTS TEST CONFIGURATION (Optional - only needed for real webhook testing)
# ===================================================================
#
# If not provided, tests will use mock payment responses (API calls work, but webhooks won't)
# For full end-to-end testing with real CloudPayments checkout + webhooks, provide these:
#
# CLOUDPAYMENTS_PUBLIC_ID=pk_YOUR_TEST_PUBLIC_ID_HERE
# CLOUDPAYMENTS_API_SECRET=YOUR_TEST_API_SECRET_HERE

# ===================================================================
# NOTES
# ===================================================================
# - LiveKit is automatically started with test configuration
# - This file is only needed if you want to test with REAL CloudPayments checkout + webhooks
